Description_lang: When Rapid Fire finishes channeling, the time between your Auto Shots is reduced by ${-$407405s1/1000}.1 sec for $407405d.

description_blz.en_US: When Rapid Fire finishes channeling, the time between your Auto Shots is reduced by 1.0 sec for 12 sec.

description_blz.ko_KR: 속사의 정신 집중이 끝나면 12초 동안 자동 사격 간격이 1.0초만큼 감소합니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 急速射擊引導完成時，你的自動射擊間隔縮短1.0秒，持續12秒。
